      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Hybrid retrieval (pgvector + BM25 + trigram, RRF fused)\nfeeds the picker.\n\nPicker SEES: description, value, currency, qty, weight, origin\nPicker DOES NOT SEE: merchant_code\n\nReturns: top-1 + top-3 alts + confidence + GIR rationale",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hybrid retrieval (pgvector + BM25 + trigram, RRF fused)\nfeeds the picker.\n\nPicker SEES: description, value, currency, qty, weight, origin\nPicker DOES NOT SEE: merchant_code\n\nReturns: top-1 + top-3 alts + confidence + GIR rationale",
      "lineHeight": 1.3
    },
